      "message": "Hey Wayne, I just ran a gating for your change and `drools-pdp` [is in a crashing state](https://logs.onap.org/onap-integration/gating/142581-2/infrastructure-healthcheck/k8s-teardown/k8s-teardown/index.html).\nThe issue [seems to be caused by](https://logs.onap.org/onap-integration/gating/142581-2/infrastructure-healthcheck/k8s-teardown/k8s-teardown/pod-onap-policy-drools-pdp-0-policy-drools-pdp-logs.html) invalid permissions for the entrypoint script:\n\n```\nsh: /opt/app/policy/bin/pdpd-cl-entrypoint.sh: Permission denied\n```",
